{"tid":2214784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"某電視台力推東莞經濟圈，行為本質就是莞獨份子搞政治噱頭，暗藏分裂國家意圖","createTime":"2020-09-23T13:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T13:28:54.000Z","uid":98391,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a22e7d6b347bbb24120cbebe275911cf2cf44a","tid":2214784,"uid":98391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">呢排TVB黃金時段同埋東張西望有個廣告，叫做CAMS凱武士「双肩包」</span></strong>，屌你老尾搵個鬼佬扮科學家拍廣告，講到甚麼權威認證，但其實係東莞製造，乜乜東莞本土品牌，亦無外國勢力認可，係搵間發生過「學術造假」既西安大學做認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnJA3xA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnJA3xA.png&h=01f4bb39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">TVB越大力推祟，我地就越要拆穿佢假面具</span></span></strong>，見佢宣傳咁多，又有美心妹妹幫手宣傳，<strong><span class=\"red\">應該落咗好多廣告費，我地千其千其要派嬲😡</span></strong>，比多啲家長知道唔好五、六舊水買錯東莞貨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">😡 CAMS凱武士双肩包 😡</span></strong><br />\r<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CAMSBackpack/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCAMSBackpack%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9syZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=e19e02ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CAMSBackpack/</a><br />\r<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eiELEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eiELEF.png&h=e0b3f971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrFjLOk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrFjLOk.png&h=62be2fb6&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\r<em><strong><span class=\"orange\">「東莞本土的本質就是搞保護主義、單邊主義，與『習思想』相違背、開歷史倒車的人注定不會成功（抵制TVB民間團隊，2020）。」</span></strong></em><br />\r\n============================================<br />\r<blockquote><p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\